## ğŸ§­ 1. Overview

**Purpose**
BizGenius is a comprehensive mobile-first business learning application that empowers users with AI-driven tools to learn business skills, generate custom business plans, and interact with a smart business assistant. It targets aspiring entrepreneurs, small business owners, and students.

