## ğŸ¯ 2. Goals and Objectives

* Deliver real-time business advice using an AI-powered chatbot
* Generate custom, downloadable business plans via OpenAI/Open route
* Educate users through structured video tutorials and interactive content
* Track progress, save notes, and improve over time via analytics and AI updates

---

## ğŸ‘¤ 3. Target Audience

* Entrepreneurs & startup founders
