## ğŸ”‘ 4. Key Features

### ğŸ§  AI-Powered Business Assistant

* Integration with **OpenAI API** (GPT-4o or GPT-4.5)
* Users can ask questions on:

  * Marketing, Finance, Strategy, Operations
* Features:

  * Real-time intelligent responses
  * Save chat history & bookmark important answers
  * Categorized Q\&A view (searchable)

---

### ğŸ“„ Business Plan Generator

* AI-generated, editable business plan builder
* Sections included:

  * Executive Summary
  * Market Analysis
  * Financial Projections
  * Marketing Strategy
  * Operations Plan
  * Management Structure
* Customizable by:

  * Business size (Startup, SME, Corporation)
  * Industry (Tech, Agriculture, Retail, etc.)
* Export options:

  * PDF
  * DOCX (Word)
  * PPTX (PowerPoint)

---

### ğŸ“ Learning Hub

* Structured **video learning platform**
* Features:

  * Categorized tutorials (e.g., Finance, Startup, Marketing, Legal)
  * Step-by-step business planning guides
  * Real-world expert interviews
  * Case studies and real examples
  * Interactive quizzes per module
  * Progress tracking dashboard
  * Bookmarks and note-taking
  * Offline mode (downloadable content)

