## ğŸ› ï¸ 5. Technical Requirements

| Feature             | Description                                                                   |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Platform**        | Web App (Mobile Responsive) + Mobile App (future phase)                       |
| **Frontend**        | React , Tailwind CSS                                       |
| **Backend**         |  Supabase                                              |
| **Auth**            | Secure User Authentication (OAuth, Email/Password)                            |
| **Database**        | PostgreSQL (via Supabase )                                         |
| **AI Integration**  | OpenAI API (GPT-4)  or open router Api                                                           |
| **Cloud Storage**   | For plans, notes, and video  (Supabase Storage) |
| **Video Streaming** | HLS Streaming or Vimeo/YouTube private APIs                                   |
| **Analytics**       | Custom analytics dashboard (learning progress, quiz scores, time spent)       |
| **Exporting**       | Dynamic PDF/DOCX/PPTX generation (via Puppeteer or docx-pdf libraries)        |
| **Offline Access**  | LocalStorage + IndexedDB for caching downloaded content                       |
| **CMS**             | Admin panel for adding/updating learning content                              |

